WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:04.600
The reason why my Bai family broke off the marriage

2
00:00:04.600 --> 00:00:05.933
It's all made by Luojia Factory

3
00:00:05.933 --> 00:00:07.766
That wasn't my intention at all.

4
00:00:07.766 --> 00:00:11.800
All the families your Bai family made friends with before Bai

5
00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:13.500
This is all done by my Lu family

6
00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:16.433
How dare you betray me now, Mr. Lu?

7
00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:18.000
Don't be rich and stubborn

8
00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:20.866
If you make a mistake, you will stand at attention and be beaten, apologize and beg for mercy

9
00:00:21.133 --> 00:00:22.100
And this marriage

10
00:00:22.100 --> 00:00:24.433
It was originally your Lu family who repaired first and retreated

11
00:00:26.266 --> 00:00:26.866
That Zhou Xun

12
00:00:26.866 --> 00:00:28.133
Oh no, not raw.

13
00:00:28.133 --> 00:00:32.633
Sir, the return of my Wang family is also coordinated by the Ye family.

14
00:00:33.100 --> 00:00:35.166
Please spare my Wang family's life

15
00:00:35.166 --> 00:00:37.266
Wang Yueru, what do you mean?

16
00:00:37.400 --> 00:00:41.333
War God Ye, please see from a distance that this punishment is too severe

17
00:00:41.333 --> 00:00:42.466
Kneel down and beg for mercy

18
00:00:42.466 --> 00:00:43.366
There's a silver lining.

19
00:00:43.366 --> 00:00:45.100
This is if you die hard

20
00:00:45.333 --> 00:00:47.266
I want to die without a corpse

21
00:00:48.200 --> 00:00:50.766
Please let my Liu family go

22
00:00:51.766 --> 00:00:53.033
And my Jiang family

23
00:00:53.333 --> 00:00:54.466
And my Zhu family

24
00:00:54.466 --> 00:00:55.633
beg for mercy

25
00:00:55.766 --> 00:00:56.966
wishful thinking

26
00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:59.666
There have been so many opportunities given to you that you do not cherish

27
00:00:59.666 --> 00:01:01.200
Now one by one is suffering

28
00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:02.600
Now it's like a dog.

29
00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:04.133
Kneel down with your tail between your legs

30
00:01:04.133 --> 00:01:05.166
Please

31
00:01:05.166 --> 00:01:06.966
In front of playing hometown

32
00:01:07.133 --> 00:01:09.700
But we have taken all the houses that should be collected.

33
00:01:09.700 --> 00:01:11.133
Can't you just leave us alone?

34
00:01:11.133 --> 00:01:13.800
Yes, we've already said sorry.

35
00:01:13.800 --> 00:01:15.866
Can't you be quick with me?

36
00:01:15.866 --> 00:01:17.600
Obviously you were wrong first

37
00:01:17.733 --> 00:01:19.800
Now they are still wronged one by one

38
00:01:19.800 --> 00:01:21.033
I'm sorry.

39
00:01:21.066 --> 00:01:23.266
I just want to get rid of all the evil that came before

40
00:01:23.266 --> 00:01:24.233
I'll tell you what.

41
00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:25.500
Absolutely impossible

42
00:01:25.500 --> 00:01:27.800
This is you moving into a rock and smashing yourself in the foot.

43
00:01:27.800 --> 00:01:29.766
It's you who don't cry without seeing the coffin

44
00:01:29.766 --> 00:01:31.900
Don't die until you reach the Yellow River

